# **Website Content & ERP Integration**

## **1\. Website Overview & ERP Integration**

### **1.1 Website Purpose**

Mastercraftworld (MCW) will operate as a **fully digital platform** for **on-demand maintenance services, corporate supply, and SaaS-based facility management tools**. The website will feature **ERP integration** to manage invoices, estimations, vendor registrations, corporate contracts, and training enrollments.

### **1.2 Core Functionalities**

✅ **Service Booking & Quotation Management** (Instant estimates, custom project quotes)  
✅ **Automated Invoicing & ERP Sync** (For corporate clients & vendors)  
✅ **Vendor & Corporate Registration System** (Automated onboarding)  
✅ **Training & Certification Enrollment** (Direct registration & e-learning)  
✅ **B2B E-commerce for Hardware & Supplies** (Marketplace for corporate trading)  
✅ **AI-Powered Digital Marketing & User Analytics** (SEO, Ads, Customer Tracking)

## **2\. Website Structure & Page Content**

### **2.1 Home Page**

📌 **Welcome Message:**

“Welcome to Mastercraftworld – The Future of Maintenance & Trading Solutions\! Book services, get instant quotations, manage invoices, or register as a vendor. All from one digital-first platform.”

**Key Sections:**

* 🌟 **Instant Service Booking:** Select **plumbing, electrical, or facility management** services.  
* 🏢 **Corporate Registration:** Companies can sign up for **B2B supply & contracts**.  
* 📜 **Get an Estimate:** Customers can request a **real-time quotation**.  
* 🚀 **Training & Certification Enrollment:** Individuals register for **technical training**.  
* 🏭 **Supplier/Vendor Registration:** Suppliers register to list products on MCW.  
* 📊 **ERP Dashboard Login:** Secure login for **corporate clients & vendors**.

### **2.2 About Us**

📌 **Who We Are:** Mastercraftworld (MCW) is a **tech-driven on-demand service & supply platform**. We connect individuals and businesses with **trusted service providers, vendors, and corporate suppliers**.

📌 **Our Mission:** ✔️ **Revolutionizing maintenance services & corporate supply** via a digital-first approach.  
✔️ **Empowering SMEs & enterprises** with **automated invoice & estimation tools**.  
✔️ **Providing AI-driven analytics** for operational efficiency.

📌 **How We Work:** ✅ **95% Outsourced Resources** → Service providers & logistics partners handle fulfillment.  
✅ **5% Internal Resources** → MCW supervises quality control & compliance.  
✅ **AI-Powered Matching** → Smart algorithms connect users with the best service providers.
